eb/20201229052931/https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85-%E6%9B%BE%E5%B0%8D%E5%85%A8%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4%E6%9C%89%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%E8%B2%A2%E7%8D%BB-%E5%8F%AF%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8C%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92/ |archivedate=2020-12-29 |language= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。整個建築共有100條柱，當中22條藏在水缸內，其餘78條外露<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/society/主教山減壓缸部分被拆毀-文物保育專員道歉稱-溝通敏感度不足-避答古蹟辦曾否看圖則及視察/|title=主教山配水庫被拆　文物保育專員道歉　證三年前水務署曾諮詢　當時判斷只屬「一個水缸」|author=|date=2020-12-29|work=|publisher=立場新聞|accessdate=2020-12-30|language=|format=|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101024834/https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E6%B8%9B%E5%A3%93%E7%BC%B8%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%86%E6%AF%80-%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E4%BF%9D%E8%82%B2%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E7%A8%B1-%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E5%BA%A6%E4%B8%8D%E8%B6%B3-%E9%81%BF%E7%AD%94%E5%8F%A4%E8%B9%9F%E8%BE%A6%E6%9B%BE%E5%90%A6%E7%9C%8B%E5%9C%96%E5%89%87%E5%8F%8A%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。建築方式與[[土耳其|土耳其]][[伊斯坦堡|伊斯坦堡]][[地下水宮殿|地下水宮殿]]拱形結構相近<ref>{{cite news |title=主教山配水庫已被圍封 文物學者：可成亞洲獨一無二貯水庫公園 |url=https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372600/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81-%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8C%E8%B2%AF%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92 |accessdate=2020-12-29 |agency=商業電台 |date=2020-12-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201229053425/https://www.881903.com/news/local/2372600/%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%B1%B1%E9%85%8D%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E5%B7%B2%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E5%B0%81-%E6%96%87%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E5%8F%AF%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E7%8D%A8%E4%B8%80%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%8C%E8%B2%AF%E6%B0%B4%E5%BA%AB%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92 |archivedate=2020-12-29 |language= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。水務署在1952年加建了混凝土結構<ref name=":0" />。截至清拆工程停工前，被拆毀的部份包括20乘10米面積的天花板及4條柱<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567660-20201229.htm|title=主教山食水減壓缸工程暫停　部分天花及石柱已被拆|author=|date=2020-12-29|work=即時新聞|publisher=香港電台|accessdate=2020-12-30|language=|format=|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101024952/https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567660-20201229.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發現遺址 ==
